Module PhotoCloud
Package users

Class User

java.lang.Object
users.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
FreeUser, HobbyistUser, ProfessionalUser
public abstract class User extends Object
Abstract User class serves as a template for all user types. It holds general user data such as name, email, and profile picture, and provides basic functionality for interacting with the user's data.
